hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4869f26986c7088a2646055a9a89aa4abcce89ea","tid":765091,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:32:59.000Z","msg":"干預內政"},{"pid":"e0db1d914f31de77bdaf4db04a5d15068a51cabc","tid":765091,"uid":40588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"87660308137f0ddaadce04f619cc46a8b2f6b2c5","tid":765091,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d3d130be02693ab1e673e9e1b2635d0c6d99038","tid":765091,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecac07c1b7eaee0a1405b056edf38951608d2fd2","tid":765091,"uid":40588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T19:37:31.000Z","msg":"聽講有支那廠掛日本國旗添"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/japan.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2Fjapan.png&h=49dad728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越南排華,海爾掛日本旗避難<br />\n<br />\n中越局勢緊張，當地中資企業為求自保，方法層出不窮。有日本新聞台在5月19日上載了一段新聞片段，當中發現中國著名的電器巨擘海爾 (Haier)，其設于越南的工廠上，懷疑同時掛上日本國旗及越南國旗：<br />\n<br />\n　 海爾集團目前在全球各地建立21個工業區，根據其官網所示，於2013年的集團利潤為108億元，其創始地在青島，是一家中國企業，目前並沒有日資參與；而在2011年，海爾宣布從日本家電品牌松下手中收購了三洋電機，當中包括越南的電器業務，根據新浪網5月16日報道，海爾集團在2012年4月的越南工廠開始營運，工廠佔地7.7萬平方米，以生產雪櫃及洗衣機為主。<br />\n<br />\n　　內地網民並開始此事議論紛紛，主要討論區包括天涯、百度貼吧皆引起熱話，不少網民表示日後會抵制海爾貨品，認為事件如果屬實，將嚴重打撃中國政府的威信，當中的言論包括「中國政府可以保護誰願意掛鬼子旗」、「中國的臉又一次被搧」、「我再也不買海爾了」等。"},{"pid":"754c91a2996df1b03b636f1ee4f9b35636f56e95","tid":765091,"uid":3223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:23:30.000Z","msg":"越南識玩"},{"pid":"8d09e0072d4fec661a833ef9843e2bc826409bdb","tid":765091,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:25:05.000Z","msg":"自己一身蟻<br />\n仲走去管支𣄃仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞掂自己個檔口先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b351e016bb253e9c9cf9b79973df596c04e32ac6","tid":765091,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469a65264eca52ff6bc13a4070888c9deac90b39","tid":765091,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca947f232ad04ed8884707c6af1cb7b1971d8aef","tid":765091,"uid":110734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3be2ec75c10da02f85da27a4807bfea41f5352be","tid":765091,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94f8524acf62d22cf283902940b53a233aad9e38","tid":765091,"uid":43173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T19:36:14.000Z","msg":"喺人地國家又唔係掛你支旗都要管,係咪飲撚大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T22:33:41.000Z","msg":"因為支那當自己係蘇聯之後嘅共產國家老大哥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T22:47:14.000Z","msg":"共你老母產咩，佢地洗緊人民幣呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:48:17.000Z","msg":"你其實係咪唔明我意思？"}]}